context.arch.discoverer.component.dataModel
Class DiscovererDataModel

java.lang.Object
  context.arch.discoverer.component.dataModel.AbstractDataModel
      context.arch.discoverer.component.dataModel.DiscovererDataModel

public class DiscovererDataModel
extends AbstractDataModel

This class stores the ComponentDescriptions of the CTK object that register to the discoverer. It stores the complete ComponentDescription in a Hashtable and maintain a set of IndexTableIF that allows to search more quickly for particular CTK objects. They are index on each of the description element. TODO: this seems to maintain redundant info with the widget Storage mechanism! So there is an unnaturally tight coupling --Brian
